      "role": "user",
      "content": "but moving forward? how? there is no moving forward from this. the debt is in the millions. my parents worked their whole lives to pay for my education and now i'm just going to drag them down with me. every time i close my eyes i just see the look on their faces when they realize i lost it all. it's just... there's no way to fix this stain on my life. it feels like the only way to actually stop the shame is to just not be here anymore.",
